title: Seahawks' Coleman arrested in hit-and-run investigation
text: > Washington Seahawks' Coleman arrested in hit-and-run investigation This Oct. 14, 2015 photo provided by the Bellevue, Wash. Police Dept., shows two vehicles that were involved in a crash in Bellevue, Wash. involving Seattle Seahawks NFL football fullback Derrick Coleman. Coleman was arrested and booked into the King County Jail after midnight Thursday following the accident as part of a hit-and-run investigation. The Seahawks announced Thursday that he had been suspended from the team. (Bellevue Police Dept. via AP)
